{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-single-blog-js","path":"/blogs/designing-the-world-again","result":{"data":{"sanityBlog":{"title":"Designing The world Again..","_rawBody":[{"_key":"fc04d1d97237","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f9bba5a4ac1a","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"DIVIDE IT INTO SMALLER WORLD and TAKE INTO ACCOUNT:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"49d83e423a58","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c0bdf1fd4382","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b97b2637aa81","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d5674f89a12a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Sustainability: One of the most important considerations in designing the world would be to ensure that the planet is sustainable and that human activities do not harm the environment. This would involve designing systems and processes that minimize waste and pollution and that are powered by renewable energy sources."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3d22975f6b80","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"22f522e44ec90","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Equity and social justice: Another key consideration would be to design a world that is equitable and just, and that does not perpetuate social and economic inequalities. This would require creating systems that ensure access to basic needs such as food, shelter, and healthcare for all people, regardless of their background or socioeconomic status."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"6bf221a320e4","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a8b819f007fd0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Innovation and creativity: To design a world that is truly remarkable and inspiring, it would be important to encourage innovation and creativity. This could involve creating spaces and resources that enable people to experiment, take risks, and push the boundaries of what is possible."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"be4211b3d0a1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e29b5b09b2220","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Collaboration and community: Finally, designing the world would require creating systems and structures that enable collaboration and community-building. This could involve creating spaces for people to connect and work together on shared goals, and fostering a culture of empathy, understanding, and mutual support."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"coverImage":{"asset":{"gatsbyImageData":{"images":{"sources":[],"fallback":{"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?w=5568&h=3712&auto=format","srcSet":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?rect=0,2,5568,3706&w=320&h=213&auto=format 320w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?w=654&h=436&auto=format 654w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?w=768&h=512&auto=format 768w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?rect=1,0,5565,3712&w=1024&h=683&auto=format 1024w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?rect=1,0,5566,3712&w=1366&h=911&auto=format 1366w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?rect=1,0,5566,3712&w=1600&h=1067&auto=format 1600w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?w=1920&h=1280&auto=format 1920w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460e9-5568x3712.jpg?rect=0,0,5568,3711&w=2048&h=1365&auto=format 2048w,\nhttps://cdn.sanity.io/images/bmgmvqmz/production/f835e4df3c9c1327dea14d176111654712c460